: : Rodimus Prime/Kup : :

Rodimus saw Malice's attack coming and activates his back boosters. He lifts up jus above the incurring explosion. He then fires thre plasma shots down at Malice.

Kup also saw the attack coming. He transformes to truck mode and outuns the shot. He then hits his breaks, spinning around to face Malice. Kup guns it, trying to ram Malice.
